{"tid":1258126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！有個少少意見俾眾籌team","createTime":"2019-06-26T02:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T04:53:49.000Z","uid":220977,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"940df3a51efa5a4806ea71dd8f1aa309f8ad8b6b","tid":1258126,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒眾籌team 同攪炒team 幫手搞登報<br />\n<br />\n睇見英文版，台灣版，日文版既信都有十萬個人各自各係同一份稿改既問題，聽講台灣封信曾經長達3頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然話兄弟爬山，各自努力，但十萬人改同一封個google doc真係唔係好effective 同efficient， 一黎admins 又睇唔晒d comments，二黎各自改左拼貼一齊會搞到封信既文筆怪怪<br />\n<br />\n所以閣下有個少少既建議：<br />\n眾籌team assign 3-5人寫信（分語言寫），然後各版本開一個post收集意見，寫信小隊入面搵一個人負責mon post <br />\n<br />\n明白眾籌team都好辛苦，但大家都係為左條事好，話晒有咁難得既機會向國際社會講我地既訴求，大家都係想盡善盡美，唔想一不小心7出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割席，不督灰！<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"e4876410146fed38dab934695203ffc5dedfdc08","tid":1258126,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"推俾眾籌team睇"},{"pid":"18b5f03b2d4a20ad941e1809504ed1460a39893e","tid":1258126,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1291604d631d1c57bf7789dc2eec8e73fd38d67","tid":1258126,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"641aeb4884761de90eb9fb5c190c883dfc8908c0","tid":1258126,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"a3f8d672af09343b7c5a7811ad8dd8fd0de31b5f","tid":1258126,"uid":220977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"641aeb4884761de90eb9fb5c190c883dfc8908c0","tid":1258126,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"